<item>
            <title>[LU-4566] Downgrade lustre version from lustre 1.8.9 to 1.8.7</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4566</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For testing purpose, we want to downgrade our lustre environment to version 1.8.7 starting from 1.8.9. Is this operation supported and without risks? &lt;br/&gt;
regards&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>redhat 5.7&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
lustre-1.8.9-2.6.18_348.3.1.el5_lustre.g0667314_g7880158&lt;br/&gt;
kernel-2.6.18-348.3.1.el5_lustre.g0667314&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
